# Sleepy AI Search backend lives in a SEPARATE GitHub repo and is
# deployed to Render from there — not from this repo. The `backend/`
# folder here is just a local reference copy for development. Keep it
# gitignored so we don't accidentally commit stale changes to the wrong
# repo, and to avoid confusion about which repo deploys to Render.
backend
